            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>官田鋼(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2017:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2017\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2017-TW</a>)29日09:49股價上漲0.62元，報9.46元，漲幅7.01%，成交3,262張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>官田鋼(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2017:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2017\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2017-TW</a>)所屬產業為鋼鐵工業，主要業務為盤元線材、球化線材、鍍鋅鐵線及螺絲之生產及買賣。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌0.11%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲4.98%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+911 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+657 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+254 張</li> <li>融資增減：+5 張</li> <li>融券增減：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
